overview:
English Profi is a job board and directory for the niche market of language services.

Freelancers and agencies market their services to companies and the public. Each member has a profile featuring their services, experience and prices. As freelancers become more and more important in the global economy, they need specialized sites where they can be easily found. English Profi focuses on the language of global business. Search English Profi for translators, interpreters, English as a second language trainers, copywriters, localization experts and voice over actors. Each of these professions are distinct and unique yet there is also overlap in many cases. When you need someone specialized in language services, search the English Profi data base or just post a job and wait for candidates to come to you.
